---
---
<section class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-slate-50" id="comparativo">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    
    <div class="text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-12 md:mb-16 px-4 sm:px-0">
      <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-[#0A2F5C] mb-4 md:mb-6 leading-tight">
        A armadilha do piso cerâmico/porcelanato
      </h2>
      <p class="text-base md:text-lg text-slate-600 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
        Sair do tradicional pode ser muito mais eficiente. Compare, entenda e faça uma escolha inteligente!
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="flex md:grid md:grid-cols-2 overflow-x-auto md:overflow-visible snap-x snap-mandatory gap-6 md:gap-8 pb-8 md:pb-0 hide-scrollbar -mx-4 px-4 md:mx-auto md:px-0 max-w-4xl items-stretch">
      
      <div class="snap-center shrink-0 w-[85%] md:w-auto bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 md:p-8 border-t-4 border-red-500 shadow-sm text-left flex flex-col">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 mb-6 flex items-center">
          <span class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-red-100 text-red-600 flex items-center justify-center mr-3 text-sm flex-shrink-0">✕</span>
          A dor do piso cerâmico
        </h3>
        <ul class="space-y-5">
          <li class="flex items-start text-sm md:text-base text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
            <span class="mr-3 text-red-500 font-bold mt-0.5">✗</span> Semanas de quebra-quebra, poeira e entulho na sua casa nova.
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start text-sm md:text-base text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
            <span class="mr-3 text-red-500 font-bold mt-0.5">✗</span> Risco alto do piso soltar, trincar ou ficar desnivelado.
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start text-sm md:text-base text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
            <span class="mr-3 text-red-500 font-bold mt-0.5">✗</span> Frio ao toque e acústica ruim (eco nos ambientes).
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="snap-center shrink-0 w-[85%] md:w-auto bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 md:p-8 border-t-4 border-[#B28D42] shadow-xl relative text-left flex flex-col">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-[#0A2F5C] mb-6 flex items-center">
          <span class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-[#0A2F5C]/10 text-[#B28D42] flex items-center justify-center mr-3 text-sm flex-shrink-0">✓</span>
          A inteligência Cas4
        </h3>
        <ul class="space-y-5">
          <li class="flex items-start text-sm md:text-base text-slate-700 font-medium leading-relaxed">
            <span class="mr-3 text-[#B28D42] text-lg leading-none mt-0.5">✓</span> Instalação cirúrgica e limpa, muitas vezes finalizada em 1 dia.
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start text-sm md:text-base text-slate-700 font-medium leading-relaxed">
            <span class="mr-3 text-[#B28D42] text-lg leading-none mt-0.5">✓</span> Zero entulho. Feito para entrar na fase final da pintura.
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start text-sm md:text-base text-slate-700 font-medium leading-relaxed">
            <span class="mr-3 text-[#B28D42] text-lg leading-none mt-0.5">✓</span> Conforto térmico absoluto e visual sofisticado de madeira.
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>